<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Command Documentation - CertiFried Announcer</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css?v=1.3.7">
</head>
<body class="bg-dark text-white">
    <%- include('partials/header-landing') %>
    <div class="container mt-4 mb-5">
        <div class="text-center mb-5">
            <h1><i class="fas fa-book me-2"></i>Command Documentation</h1>
            <p class="lead command-page-subtitle">A complete guide to all available slash commands. Required permissions are labeled for each command.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="row g-4">
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <div class="command-card">
                    <h4><i class="fas fa-star me-2 text-warning"></i>Core Setup</h4>
                    <hr>
                    <div class="command-entry"><strong>/setchannel</strong><span class="perm-badge perm-mod">Moderator</span><p class="command-description">Sets the default channel for all live announcements.</p></div>
                    <div class="command-entry"><strong>/setliverole</strong><span class="perm-badge perm-mod">Moderator</span><p class="command-description">Sets a role to be assigned to linked Discord users when they go live.</p></div>
                    <div class="command-entry"><strong>/setup-requests</strong><span class="perm-badge perm-admin">Admin</span><p class="command-description">Posts a panel for server members to request their own streams.</p></div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                 <div class="command-card">
                    <h4><i class="fas fa-paint-brush me-2"></i>Customization</h4>
                    <hr>
                    <div class="command-entry"><strong>/customize-streamer</strong><span class="perm-badge perm-mod">Moderator</span><p class="command-description">**The power tool!** Sets a unique webhook name, avatar, or message for a streamer in a *specific channel*.</p></div>
                    <div class="command-entry"><strong>/customize-channel</strong><span class="perm-badge perm-mod">Moderator</span><p class="command-description">Sets a default webhook name/avatar for *all* announcements in a specific channel.</p></div>
                    <div class="command-entry"><strong>/customize-bot</strong><span class="perm-badge perm-mod">Moderator</span><p class="command-description">Changes the bot's default nickname or announcement avatar for this server.</p></div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-12">
                <div class="command-card">
                    <h4><i class="fas fa-user-plus me-2"></i>Streamer Management</h4>
                    <hr>
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-lg-6">
                            <div class="command-entry"><strong>/addstreamer & /removestreamer</strong><span class="perm-badge perm-mod">Moderator</span><p class="command-description">Adds or removes a single streamer from the notification list and purges their announcements.</p></div>
                            <div class="command-entry"><strong>/liststreamers & /check-live</strong><span class="perm-badge perm-mod">Moderator</span><p class="command-description">Lists all tracked streamers, or only those currently live.</p></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-lg-6">
                           <p><strong>/addstreamer Options:</strong></p>
                            <ul class="option-list small">
                                <li><code>platform</code>: The streaming platform.</li>
                                <li><code>username</code>: The streamer's name or channel ID.</li>
                                <li><code>user</code>: (Optional) The Discord user to link for the Live Role.</li>
                                <li><code>avatar</code>: (Optional) A custom avatar for this streamer's webhook announcements.</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
             <div class="col-12">
                 <div class="command-card">
                    <h4><i class="fas fa-rocket me-2 text-danger"></i>Bulk & Team Actions</h4>
                    <hr>
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-lg-6">
                            <div class="command-entry"><strong>/addteam</strong><span class="perm-badge perm-mod">Moderator</span><p class="command-description"><strong>(One-Time Add)</strong> Adds all current members of a Twitch Team to a specific channel.</p></div>
                            <div class="command-entry"><strong>/removeteam</strong><span class="perm-badge perm-mod">Moderator</span><p class="command-description"><strong>(One-Time Remove)</strong> Removes all members of a Twitch Team from a channel and purges their announcements.</p></div>
                            <div class="command-entry"><strong>/subscribe-team</strong><span class="perm-badge perm-mod">Moderator</span><p class="command-description"><strong>(Automated)</strong> Automatically keeps a channel synced with a Twitch Team.</p></div>
                            <div class="command-entry"><strong>/unsubscribe-team</strong><span class="perm-badge perm-mod">Moderator</span><p class="command-description">Stops the automatic syncing for a team on a channel.</p></div>
                        </div>
                         <div class="col-lg-6">
                            <div class="command-entry"><strong>/importteamcsv</strong><span class="perm-badge perm-mod">Moderator</span><p class="command-description">**Syncs** a channel with a CSV, adding/updating members from the file and removing members not in it.</p></div>
                            <div class="command-entry"><strong>/importcsv & /exportcsv</strong><span class="perm-badge perm-mod">Moderator</span><p class="command-description">Adds/updates or exports all streamer data using a <code>.csv</code> file.</p></div>
                            <div class="command-entry"><strong>/massaddstreamer & /massremovestreamer</strong><span class="perm-badge perm-mod">Moderator</span><p class="command-description">Adds or removes a comma-separated list of streamers and purges their announcements.</p></div>
                            <div class="command-entry"><strong>/clearstreamers</strong><span class="perm-badge perm-admin">Admin</span><p class="command-description">Removes **ALL** streamers and purges **ALL** announcements from the server.</p></div>
                       </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
             <div class="col-12 text-center mt-4">
                <p class="lead command-page-subtitle">For easier management, you can access the <a href="/dashboard" target="_blank">Web Dashboard</a> to control everything visually.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>